                        Opposition is either contradictory of a particular to an universall;
or contrary, of an universall to an universall; or subcontrary,
of a particular negative to a particular affirmative.

                        Cap. 4. THe first and most common faculty of the Soul is the Nutritive;
by which life is in all things, the acts and operation
